parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The peeling of the original paint can lead to exposure of the primer, which can cause corrosion and damage to the vehicle's body, potentially affecting its structural integrity and safety.
symptoms: The paint is peeling off in several locations
including the hood
doors
and roof; the paint is bubbling and flaking off
exposing the primer; the paint is chipping
especially in areas with two-tone colors.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Tread Separation in Continental General Amer GHS Tires
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Tread separation can lead to loss of vehicle control, accidents, and injuries, especially at high speeds.
symptoms: Tread separation
damage to surrounding vehicle components (e.g.
exhaust system
truck bed)
potential loss of vehicle control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rusting and corrosion of the fuel tank can lead to fuel leaks, electrical shorts, and potentially cause a fire, resulting in serious safety risks to the occupants and other road users.
symptoms: Rust or corrosion visible on the fuel tank
fuel leaks
electrical issues
sparks or arcing near the fuel tank
hole or perforation on the top of the tank near electrical wires.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Electrical System Failure Leading to Engine Compartment Fires
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: An electrical system failure can cause a fire to break out in the engine compartment, potentially resulting in a total loss of the vehicle and posing a significant risk to the safety of the occupants and other road users.
symptoms: Smoke or flames emanating from under the hood or engine compartment
burning smell
loss of engine power
warning lights or alarms on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Transmission Slipping and Failure to Shift
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission slipping and failure to shift can cause loss of control, accidents, and engine damage, leading to costly repairs and potentially leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle fails to shift gears
the engine revs excessively
the transmission slips
the vehicle hesitates or stutters while shifting
the transmission warning light illuminates on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Repeated transmission replacements can lead to extended downtime, increased repair costs, and continued safety risks due to the potential for the new transmission to fail as well.
symptoms: The transmission needs to be replaced multiple times
the vehicle experiences recurring transmission problems after replacement
the transmission warning light illuminates on the dashboard after replacement.
